00:52:10.860 --> 00:52:12.630
was actually a moving thing.

00:52:12.630 --> 00:52:13.620
Glass is liquid.

00:52:13.620 --> 00:52:15.150
It's always moving.

00:52:15.150 --> 00:52:19.350
And so it settles down to
the bottom of the window.

00:52:19.350 --> 00:52:20.610
We're a bit like that.

00:52:20.610 --> 00:52:24.540
We're a moving thing that
looks kind of solid actually,

00:52:24.540 --> 00:52:29.110
